<p><i><b>Robert's Rules of Order</b></i> is the informal short title of a book containing <a href="/wiki/Rules_of_order" title="Rules of order">rules of order</a> intended to be adopted for use by a <a href="/wiki/Deliberative_assembly" title="Deliberative assembly">deliberative assembly</a>.</p>
